tatami.core.agent.visualization

Interface AgentGui.InputListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClaimBehavior
    Enclosing interface:
    AgentGui

    public static interface AgentGui.InputListener
    This interface should be implemented by classes that are able to receive notifications from 'active' inputs. Such notifications will be accompanied by some arguments describing the notification, beside the name of the component generating the notification.
    Author:
    Andrei Olaru
